{"word":"ἐντρέπω","slug":"ἐντρέπω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐντρέπω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐν\">ἐν</a>, τρέπω</el> ‘turn’; ‘turn about’ relating to change of position or condition] in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> in extended sense of ‘turn about’<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘put to shame’, <b>shame <a href='B:530 4:14'>1 Cor 4:14</a>; <a href='B:600 3:14'>2 Th 3:14</a>; <a href='B:630 2:8'>Tit 2:8</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘have regard for’, <b>respect <a href='B:470 21:37'>Mt 21:37</a>; <a href='B:480 12:6'>Mk 12:6</a>; <a href='B:490 18:2'>Lk 18:2</a>, <a href='B:490 18:4'>4</a></b> (in these two <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ vss.\">vss.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄνθρωπος\">ἄνθρωπος</a></el> be a respecter of persons); <b><a href='B:490 20:13'>20:13</a>; <a href='B:650 12:9'>Hb 12:9</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐντραπῇ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐντρέφω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}